snippet.title: LFS Mods Trailer
snippet.description:
A first look at a few possibilities created using our new mods system, available soon!
Video by Michal Málek. Three wheeler by Martin Kapal. Old style GP car and E-Challenger by Michal Málek. Safety car mod, football stadium layout and InSim by Chris McElroy.
